Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs42}重複緊急狀態
